originalText.text: The most horrible booking company with the most terrible costumer service! I learned my lesson never ‘trying’  these companies again!! Please STAY AWAY if you don’t want regrets!

originalText.text: The representatives for this agency are extremely rude and unprofessional. Do not waste your time this site is a SCAM, stay away from them! They advertise fair ticket prices, and once the consumer is done booking they call you within a day and tell you the fare you have selected is no longer available or they can help book an "identical itinerary" for 30-40% more than the price initially offered. Luckily I caught on before it happen again for the third time within a short span of time.

originalText.text:
Worst place to get a  cheap ticket and flight. They take all your  card information  and then don't give ur information  for the flight you book and when you  call them  they just want to charge you double the price than what you saw online. Take it from me  do not go to buy on this website it's  a SCAM!!!!
(Edit) What they don't tell you is its like a game first come first served so as soon as you fill out the info  you have to wait in order to see if you get the flight or not
In a short summary it depends on where your going.
